        <h3>Why predictive modelling?</h3>
        <p>In the present day, multiple diagnostic tests involve exorbitant cost and are not affordable for everyone. Because of this, medical tests are often not conducted at an early stage. This website aims to offer "predictive diagnosis" for certain health conditions based on mathematical concepts — predictions arrived at using simple lab test results and other factors like lifestyle and family history. As a first step towards that objective, prediction of menopause onset has been worked out here.</p>
      </article>

